     <p class="maintext"><a href="home/pauling2.html">Orthomolecular Psychiatry</a> by<em> </em>Linus Pauling, Ph.D.</p> 
     <p class="maintext"><a href="home/wund.html">Orthomolecular Medicine - Revisited<em> </em></a>by Ray C. Wunderlich, Jr., M.D.<em><a href="wund.html"> </a></em></p> 
